---
title: Cheesy Baked Pasta and Pork Sausage Meatballs with Spinach
description: Tonight's plate of pasta is a baked riff on spaghetti and meatballs. Penne tossed in tomato sauce and spinach is topped with pork meatballs before being layered with a generous helping of cheese and going under the broiler for a crispy finish!
